1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 13=

19
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:36,980
You're awake.

20
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:39,700
Your Majesty.

21
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:41,730
Were you here the whole night?

22
00:01:42,250 --> 00:01:43,930
You were hurt because of me.

23
00:01:44,130 --> 00:01:45,129
Of course,

24
00:01:45,130 --> 00:01:46,370
I would stay by your side.

25
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:48,090
Promise me.

26
00:01:48,180 --> 00:01:50,140
You must never risk your life
for me again.

27
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:52,170
I...

28
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:54,090
I'm sorry.

29
00:01:55,050 --> 00:01:55,650
I...

30
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,849
I wasn't reproaching you.

31
00:01:58,850 --> 00:01:59,980
It's just that

32
00:02:00,050 --> 00:02:01,290
I hate seeing you hurt.

33
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:04,420
It breaks my heart.

34
00:02:13,930 --> 00:02:14,900
I've been so occupied

35
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:17,900
with court affairs

36
00:02:20,050 --> 00:02:21,620
that I never understood
how you truly felt.

37
00:02:22,810 --> 00:02:23,900
I've neglected you.

38
00:02:26,300 --> 00:02:27,130
Your Majesty.

39
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:44,649
The man we caught last night

40
00:02:44,650 --> 00:02:45,900
confessed everything.

41
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,000
(Wang Cheng's Confession)

42
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:50,460
This is outrageous.

43
00:02:51,140 --> 00:02:53,609
Someone's actually dealing drugs in Jing.
They sell Fushou Cream.

44
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:55,850
No wonder the Zuixian House
is packed every day.

45
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:57,340
Once you're hooked,

46
00:02:57,810 --> 00:02:59,299
it'll bankrupt families

47
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,650
and tear them apart.

48
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:03,090
Given Jing's climate and soil,

49
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,500
we can't grow such a crop here.

50
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:06,810
The Fushou Cream

51
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:08,500
must've come from the Western Yi.

52
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:14,240
I can't believe someone
sold out the country for personal gain,

53
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:18,060
working with foreign barbarians
to bring this drug into Jing.

54
00:03:18,370 --> 00:03:19,810
We suspected all along

55
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:22,250
that Zuixian House had powerful backers.

56
00:03:22,300 --> 00:03:24,410
Now we've found Fushou Cream here.

57
00:03:26,330 --> 00:03:28,250
The mastermind

58
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:31,500
must be someone inside the court.

59
00:03:35,130 --> 00:03:36,880
Without protection
from high-ranking officials,

60
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:40,020
there's no way it could've
reached the capital so easily

61
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:41,930
and been sold so openly.

62
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:44,500
Corruption can be punished.

63
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:46,300
Fractional strife can be dealt with.

64
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:47,580
But drug trafficking

65
00:03:48,050 --> 00:03:50,410
can bring down an entire nation.

66
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:52,410
Bei,

67
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,529
we both know
how devastating drugs can be.

68
00:03:54,530 --> 00:03:55,900
The current situation

69
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:58,250
is no longer about
the two of us surviving.

70
00:03:58,700 --> 00:03:59,850
It's about

71
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:01,250
the nation

72
00:04:01,930 --> 00:04:03,220
and its people.

73
00:04:03,930 --> 00:04:05,650
We have to expose

74
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:07,650
the mastermind

75
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:10,300
and wipe out this scourge
once and for all.

76
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:14,930
Bei,

77
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:18,530
I know you want a carefree and easy life.

78
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:20,650
Yet I keep dragging you

79
00:04:21,170 --> 00:04:22,730
into all these intrigues.

80
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,650
Even if I enjoy an easy life,

81
00:04:26,770 --> 00:04:28,209
I know there can be no peace

82
00:04:28,210 --> 00:04:30,460
when the country is in turmoil.

83
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:32,020
Taking it easy isn't giving up.

84
00:04:32,580 --> 00:04:35,460
I simply refuse
to be consumed by the world.

85
00:04:37,290 --> 00:04:39,650
I don't work hard
to win any competition either.

86
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:44,490
I do it

87
00:04:46,290 --> 00:04:47,940
to protect the people I care about.

88
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:03,040
(Zuixian House, The Best Massage Parlor)

89
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:14,729
That's all?

90
00:05:14,730 --> 00:05:15,459
Where is the rest?

91
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:16,409
No more.

92
00:05:16,410 --> 00:05:17,290
That's everything.

93
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:18,700
Impossible.

94
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:21,900
Zuixian House was doing huge business.
This wouldn't even last two hours.

95
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:24,139
I've searched everywhere.

96
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:25,089
This is all I found.

97
00:05:25,090 --> 00:05:26,220
I thought it was strange too.

98
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:33,650
Where is Yan Qiu?

99
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:34,850
She escaped.

100
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:39,900
By Your Majesty's order,
we raided Zuixian House,

101
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:41,939
arrested several drug traffickers,

102
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:43,610
and seized over one jin of Fushou Cream.

103
00:05:43,770 --> 00:05:44,720
Unfortunately,

104
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:45,849
the owner of Zuixian House,

105
00:05:45,850 --> 00:05:47,649
Yan Qiu, has vanished.

106
00:05:47,650 --> 00:05:48,900
Issue a wanted notice.

107
00:05:49,210 --> 00:05:50,410
Search the entire capital.

108
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,780
Bring her in at all costs.

109
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:55,969
Your Majesty, Zuixian House
has sold Fushou Cream for a long time,

110
00:05:55,970 --> 00:05:57,729
and business has been booming.

111
00:05:57,730 --> 00:05:59,340
How could they have only one jin left?

112
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:00,769
In my humble opinion,

113
00:06:00,770 --> 00:06:02,050
they've hidden

114
00:06:02,140 --> 00:06:04,379
most of the Fushou Cream somewhere else.

115
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:06,090
Chancellor Hu makes a good point.

116
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:07,460
Gu Bei, receive my decree.

117
00:06:09,970 --> 00:06:11,780
Fushou Cream has spread
throughout the capital,

118
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:13,019
bringing ruin to the people.

119
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:15,340
I hereby appoint you Imperial Inspector

120
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:18,220
to oversee the investigation

121
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:19,820
into its trafficking.

122
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:21,490
I obey Your Majesty.

123
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:25,340
Fushou Cream

124
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,220
destroys families

125
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:28,780
and brings the nation to ruin.

126
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,220
In the name

127
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:32,169
of the Son of Heaven,

128
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:33,610
I hereby proclaim this.

129
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:35,460
Anyone involved with drugs,

130
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:37,220
official or commoner,

131
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:38,650
will be punished severely,

132
00:06:39,090 --> 00:06:40,410
without exception.

133
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:42,940
Jing

134
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:45,580
shall be free of this scourge.

135
00:06:48,170 --> 00:06:50,290
- Long live Your Majesty!
- Long live Your Majesty!

136
00:06:52,090 --> 00:06:52,780
No!

137
00:06:56,650 --> 00:06:58,380
Because of your mistake,

138
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:01,610
Fushou Cream at Zuixian House
was exposed,

139
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:03,900
and we suffered massive losses.

140
00:07:07,770 --> 00:07:09,410
I know I failed you.

141
00:07:10,170 --> 00:07:11,220
I swear,

142
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,290
from now on,

143
00:07:12,770 --> 00:07:13,409
I'll never...

144
00:07:13,410 --> 00:07:15,530
What makes you think
you'll get another chance?

145
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:36,650
Please.

146
00:07:36,850 --> 00:07:38,820
Please spare my brother.

147
00:07:38,970 --> 00:07:40,529
He's still young.

148
00:07:40,530 --> 00:07:42,410
He's just a child.

149
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:47,490
That's easy.

150
00:07:48,170 --> 00:07:49,970
Just do as you're told,

151
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:52,290
and he'll be safe.

152
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:53,820
Yes.

153
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:57,290
I'll do whatever you command, Master.

154
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,219
(Fu Qing, Consort Yu;
Shen Furong, Noble Lady Li)

155
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:09,089
(Xie Chun, Concubine Chun)

156
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:10,340
There she goes again.

157
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,820
Taking pastries to His Majesty.

158
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:15,059
Her brother was just promoted
to a First-rank General.

159
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:16,819
She has won His Majesty's favor.

160
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:18,940
She's only borrowing
her brother's prestige.

161
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:20,170
Jeez.

162
00:08:21,210 --> 00:08:23,220
If you ask me,
Gu Nan's nothing but a temptress.

163
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,840
She's wrapped His Majesty
around her finger.

164
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,530
She's not even as pretty as I am.

165
00:08:28,530 --> 00:08:30,650
I thought His Majesty
wasn't summoning anyone anymore.

166
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:33,850
Looks like I'll have to take matters
into my own hands.

167
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:35,730
Ladies,

168
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:37,420
I have something to do. Excuse me.

169
00:08:39,570 --> 00:08:41,379
(Is she going to see His Majesty?)

170
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:42,700
(I'd better beat her there.)

171
00:08:43,170 --> 00:08:45,460
Noble Lady Li, I have something urgent
to do too. I'll be off then.

172
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:49,970
Where's everyone going? Why the rush?

173
00:08:53,570 --> 00:08:54,220
Oh no!

174
00:08:54,930 --> 00:08:56,569
Are you all going to see His Majesty?

175
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:57,730
Wait for me!

176
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:05,760
(Honor Learning and Confucianism)

177
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:18,770
I've been busy

178
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,770
investigating the Fushou Cream case

179
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,300
and rooting out the drug trade.

180
00:09:22,530 --> 00:09:24,010
I've neglected you these past few days.

181
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:26,700
It's time I gave some thought
to my own matters as well.

182
00:09:27,290 --> 00:09:28,090
Your Majesty,

183
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:29,940
what's bothering you?

184
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:31,540
About my Empress.

185
00:09:31,710 --> 00:09:32,880
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

186
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,039
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

187
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,439
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

188
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:45,879
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

189
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:50,239
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

190
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:52,639
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

191
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:55,199
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

192
00:09:55,200 --> 00:10:00,879
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

193
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:06,440
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

194
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,760
♪Funny moments never stop♪

195
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,600
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

196
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:19,959
♪Yet through every up and down♪

197
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,920
♪We create miracles♪

198
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:24,680
♪From naive youths♪

199
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:27,439
♪To legendary heroes♪

200
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,359
♪This journey♪

201
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:33,399
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

202
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,920
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

203
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:41,280
♪Let's create♪

204
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:51,240
♪A legend of our own♪

